{"nodes":[{"pos":[12,49],"content":"Compiler Error C2503 | Microsoft Docs","needQuote":false,"needEscape":true,"nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Error C2503 | Microsoft Docs","pos":[0,37]}]},{"pos":[597,617],"content":"Compiler Error C2503","linkify":"Compiler Error C2503","nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Error C2503","pos":[0,20]}]},{"content":"'class' : base classes cannot contain zero-sized arrays","pos":[618,673]},{"content":"A base class or structure contains a zero-sized array.","pos":[680,734]},{"content":"An array in a class must have at least one element.","pos":[735,786]},{"content":"The following sample generates C2503:","pos":[793,830]}],"content":"---\ntitle: \"Compiler Error C2503 | Microsoft Docs\"\nms.custom: \"\"\nms.date: \"11/04/2016\"\nms.reviewer: \"\"\nms.suite: \"\"\nms.technology: \n  - \"devlang-cpp\"\nms.tgt_pltfrm: \"\"\nms.topic: \"error-reference\"\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"C2503\"\ndev_langs: \n  - \"C++\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"C2503\"\nms.assetid: da86cc89-fd04-400b-aa8d-a5ffaf7e3918\ncaps.latest.revision: 8\nauthor: \"corob-msft\"\nms.author: \"corob\"\nmanager: \"ghogen\"\ntranslation.priority.ht: \n  - \"cs-cz\"\n  - \"de-de\"\n  - \"es-es\"\n  - \"fr-fr\"\n  - \"it-it\"\n  - \"ja-jp\"\n  - \"ko-kr\"\n  - \"pl-pl\"\n  - \"pt-br\"\n  - \"ru-ru\"\n  - \"tr-tr\"\n  - \"zh-cn\"\n  - \"zh-tw\"\n---\n# Compiler Error C2503\n'class' : base classes cannot contain zero-sized arrays  \n  \n A base class or structure contains a zero-sized array. An array in a class must have at least one element.  \n  \n The following sample generates C2503:  \n  \n```  \n// C2503.cpp  \n// compile with: /c  \nclass A {  \n   public:  \n   int array [];  \n};  \n  \nclass B : A {};    // C2503  \n  \nclass C {  \npublic:  \n   int array [10];  \n};  \n  \nclass D : C {};  \n```"}